publish_ca_cert.description: Optional. When true, publishes each [CertificateAuthority][google.cloud.security.privateca.v1.CertificateAuthority]'s CA certificate and includes its URL in the "Authority Information Access" X.509 extension in all issued [Certificates][google.cloud.security.privateca.v1.Certificate].
